{"type":"message","id":"8a60555e","parentId":"3b5a9f6b","timestamp":"2026-03-24T18:54:24.967Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_drp2pfyhd2uc_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Pulse: 2026-03-24 145315\r\n\r\n## Applied Mutations\r\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\r\nRejected: experiments/cfi_freq_hybrid_experiment.ps1 (missing)\r\n\r\n## LLM Response\r\n<think>\r\nLet me analyze the current state and determine what concrete action to take.\r\n\r\nFrom the goals document, I can see:\r\n1. Phase 0 COMPLETE: Sandbox foundation established\r\n2. Phase 1 COMPLETE: Architecture cross-analysis + integration spec synthesized\r\n3. Key findings from CFI Compression Experiment\r\n4. Pending: Hybrid CFIxFreq scoring experiment (Strategy C)\r\n\r\nThe next concrete action should be to run the Hybrid CFIxFreq scoring experiment that was designed. The formula is:\r\nscore(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n\r\nThis needs to be implemented and tested against the binary thresholds to see if it better distinguishes \"constant format\" tokens (freq�160, CFI=1) from \"research trajectory\" tokens (freq<120, CFI>0.5).\r\n\r\nLet me look at what files exist that I could work with:\r\n- pulse.ps1\r\n- research/ directory files\r\n\r\nI should create a script or modify an existing file to run this experiment. Let me create a PowerShell script for the hybrid scoring experiment.\r\n\r\nThe experiment should:\r\n1. Calculate score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120) for each token\r\n2. Compare against binary thresholds (CFI � 0.5 AND freq ? [3, 120))\r\n3. Test on 200 pulses, 80/20 split\r\n\r\nLet me write a concrete script for this experiment.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe CFI Compression Synthesis identified that constant-format tokens (freq=160, CFI=1.00) are metaprogramming artifacts that need filtering. The proposed hybrid formula score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120) hasn't been tested yet.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate PowerShell script to run Hybrid CFIxFreq scoring experiment comparing the continuous scoring formula against binary thresholds, testing whether it better distinguishes constant-format from research-trajectory tokens.\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # Hybrid CFIxFreq Scoring Experiment\r\n# Strategy C: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n# Compare against binary thresholds (CFI � 0.5 AND freq ? [3, 120))\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [int]$PulseCount = 200,\r\n    [double]$TrainSplit = 0.8\r\n)\r\n\r\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Continue\"\r\n$StartTime = Get-Date\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"=== Hybrid CFIxFreq Scoring Experiment ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\nWrite-Host \"Formula: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120)\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\r\n\r\n# Load pulse history\r\n$HistoryFile = \"state/pulse_history.csv\"\r\nif (-not (Test-Path $HistoryFile)) {\r\n    Write-Host \"[ERROR] Pulse history not found: $HistoryFile\" -ForegroundColor Red\r\n    exit 1\r\n}\r\n\r\n$history = Import-Csv $HistoryFile\r\nWrite-Host \"Loaded $($history.Count) pulses from history\"\r\n\r\n# Filter to recent pulses\r\n$recent = $history | Sort-Object timestamp -Descending | Select-Object -First $PulseCount\r\nWrite-Host \"Using $($recent.Count) most recent pulses\"\r\n\r\n# Split into train/test\r\n$trainCount = [math]::Floor($recent.Count * $TrainSplit)\r\n$trainPulses = $recent | Select-Object -First $trainCount\r\n$testPulses = $recent | Select-Object -Last ($recent.Count - $trainCount)\r\nWrite-Host \"Train: $($trainPulses.Count), Test: $($testPulses.Count)\"\r\n\r\n# Analyze token frequency and CFI from training set\r\n$tokenStats = @{}\r\n\r\nforeach ($pulse in $trainPulses) {\r\n    $tokens = $pulse.tokens -split '\\s+' | Where-Object { $_ -ne \"\" }\r\n    foreach ($token in $tokens) {\r\n        if (-not $tokenStats.ContainsKey($token)) {\r\n            $tokenStats[$token] = @{\r\n                count = 0\r\n                appearances = @()\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        $tokenStats[$token].count++\r\n        $tokenStats[$token].appearances += $pulse.pulse_id\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Calculate CFI for each token\r\n$totalPulses = $trainPulses.Count\r\n$tokenAnalysis = @()\r\n\r\nforeach ($token in $tokenStats.Keys) {\r\n    $count = $tokenStats[$token].count\r\n    $cfi = $count / $totalPulses\r\n    $freq = $count\r\n    $hybridScore = $cfi * [math]::Min(1, $freq / 120)\r\n    \r\n    $tokenAnalysis += [PSCustomObject]@{\r\n        Token = $token\r\n        Freq = $freq\r\n        CFI = [math]::Round($cfi, 4)\r\n        HybridScore = [math]::Round($hybridScore, 4)\r\n        Appearances = $tokenStats[$token].appearances\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Classify using different strategies\r\n$strategyBinary = $tokenAnalysis | Where-Object { $_.CFI -ge 0.5 -and $_.Freq -ge 3 -and $_.Freq -lt 120 }\r\n$strategyHybrid = $tokenAnalysis | Where-Object { $_.HybridScore -ge 0.3 }\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"`n=== Strategy Comparison ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\nWrite-Host \"Binary (CFI�0.5 AND freq?[3,120)): $($strategyBinary.Count) tokens\"\r\nWrite-Host \"Hybrid (score�0.3): $($strategyHybrid.Count) tokens\"\r\n\r\n# Find constant-format tokens (the trap)\r\n$constantFormat = $tokenAnalysis | Where-Object { $_.Freq -ge 150 -and $_.CFI -\r\n\r\n## For Next Instantiation\r\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\r\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 14:53:36"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":481,"aggregated":"# Pulse: 2026-03-24 145315\r\n\r\n## Applied Mutations\r\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\r\nRejected: experiments/cfi_freq_hybrid_experiment.ps1 (missing)\r\n\r\n## LLM Response\r\n<think>\r\nLet me analyze the current state and determine what concrete action to take.\r\n\r\nFrom the goals document, I can see:\r\n1. Phase 0 COMPLETE: Sandbox foundation established\r\n2. Phase 1 COMPLETE: Architecture cross-analysis + integration spec synthesized\r\n3. Key findings from CFI Compression Experiment\r\n4. Pending: 